## 🏗️ ARCHITEKTURA: PLATFORM + MODULES

```
PLATFORMA (src/platform/)
  ├── auth/          — Auth (useAuth, AuthProvider)
  ├── user/          — UserState, Membership (useUserState, userStateStore)
  ├── components/    — Sdílené UI komponenty (Button, Modal, AudioPlayer...)
  ├── layouts/       — AppLayout, AppLayout s TrialExpiryModal
  ├── payments/      — Stripe checkout (useCheckout, useManageSubscription)
  └── api/           — Supabase client

MODULY (src/modules/) — samostatné produkty, lazy loaded
  ├── mvp0/          — Hlavní app (DnesPage, UcetPage, ProfilPage...)
  ├── akademie/      — Akademie modul (programy, lekce, audio)
  ├── studio/        — Studio modul (planned)
  ├── challenges/    — Výzvy modul (planned)
  └── public-web/    — Landing page, MujUcetPage (web)
```

**Kde patří kód:**
- Sdílené napříč moduly → `src/platform/`
- Specifické pro jeden modul → `src/modules/{modul}/`
- CSS pro platform komponentu → `src/styles/components/`
- CSS pro modul → `src/modules/{modul}/styles/` nebo vedle komponenty

