## 💻 CODING STANDARDS

### TypeScript:
```typescript
✅ const/let (no var), strict mode, explicit return types
✅ Interface pro objects, Type pro unions
✅ Optional chaining: user?.name
✅ Nullish coalescing: value ?? default
❌ No any — použij unknown
❌ No as casting (jen pokud nutné)
```

### React:
```typescript
✅ Functional components only
✅ Named exports (no default)
✅ Custom hooks pro logiku (useAuth, useMembership)
✅ TypeScript interfaces pro props
❌ No class components
❌ No inline styles — Tailwind třídy
❌ No prop drilling — Context/Zustand
```

### File naming:
```
Components:  PascalCase (Button.tsx, AudioPlayer.tsx)
Hooks:       camelCase (useAuth.ts, useMembership.ts)
Utils:       camelCase (formatDate.ts)
Types:       PascalCase (User.ts)
CSS:         kebab-case (button.css, audio-player.css)
```

### CSS:
```css
✅ CSS Variables z src/styles/design-tokens/
✅ Tailwind utility třídy
✅ BEM naming pro vlastní třídy (.tem-modal__title--urgent)
✅ Mobile-first media queries
❌ No !important (jen výjimečně)
❌ No inline styles
```

